title: 11 - Tom Thakkar

description: It’s our favorite boy from Bloomington, Indiana! You’ve seen him on Comedy Central, and you’ve heard from on Sirius XM and his own hit podcast with Tommy McNamara, Stand By Your Band. Now, hear his five word story! Here’s five words to describe this episode: beware your drunk alter ego.
